TITLE: Complete Custom Class Implementation in Dart
DESCRIPTION: Complete example of implementing a custom serializable class with constructor, toJson, and fromJson methods in a shared package.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/docs/06-concepts/03-serialization.md#2025-04-20_snippet_6

