TITLE: Including multiple relational objects in Serverpod
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases including multiple relational objects simultaneously using the `include` method in Serverpod. It retrieves an `Employee` object, including both the related `Address` and `Company` objects, with the `Company` object also including its related `Address`. This example demonstrates how to retrieve multiple levels of related data in a single query.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.5.0/06-concepts/06-database/07-relation-queries.md#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
"var user = await Employee.db.findById(
  session,
  employeeId,
  include: Employee.include(
    address: Address.include(),
    company: Company.include(
      address: Address.include(),
    ),
  ),
);"
```

