TITLE: Complete Main Application Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Full implementation of the main Flutter application including note management, UI components, and server communication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.1.0/05-tutorials/01-first-app.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_19

