TITLE: Implementing Image Updates Stream
DESCRIPTION: Method to create a stream of image updates for real-time client synchronization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/docs/05-tutorials/02-real-time-communication.md#2025-04-20_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
Stream imageUpdates(Session session) async* {
    var updateStream =
        session.messages.createStream<ImageUpdate>(_channelPixelAdded);

    yield ImageData(
      pixels: _pixelData.buffer.asByteData(),
      width: _imageWidth,
      height: _imageHeight,
    );

    await for (var imageUpdate in updateStream) {
      yield imageUpdate;
    }
}
```

