TITLE: Subscribing to Message Channel in Dart for Serverpod Streaming
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to subscribe to a message channel when a stream is opened. It forwards any message sent to a user identified by their user ID. The subscription is automatically disposed when the stream closes.
