TITLE: Custom Class Implementing ProtocolSerialization in Dart
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to implement the `ProtocolSerialization` interface in a custom class. It includes both `toJsonForProtocol()` and `toJson()` methods, allowing for selective serialization of fields for protocol communication. The class must implement toJsonForProtocol() to selectively serialize fields.
