SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.3.0/06-concepts/13-health-checks.md#2025-04-20_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
Future<List<ServerHealthMetric>> myHealthCheckHandler(
    Serverpod pod, DateTime timestamp) async {
  // Actually perform some checks.

  // Return a list of health metrics for the given timestamp.
  return [
    ServerHealthMetric(
      name: 'MyMetric',
      serverId: pod.serverId,
      timestamp: timestamp,
      isHealthy: true,
      value: 1.0,
    ),
  ];
}
```

