TITLE: Registering Signed-In User in Client-Side SessionManager
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to register a signed-in user in the client-side SessionManager after a successful authentication. It uses the sessionManager.registerSignedInUser method to store user information and auth token.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.2.0/06-concepts/11-authentication/04-providers/06-custom-providers.md#2025-04-20_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
