TITLE: Setting Up Message Forwarding in Stream Session - Dart
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to set up message forwarding for authenticated users by subscribing to a message channel when a stream is opened. The subscription automatically handles message routing based on user ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-0.9.22/04-concepts/09-streams.md#2025-04-20_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: dart
CODE:
```
@override
Future<void> streamOpened(StreamingSession session) async {
  session.messages.addListener(
    'user_${await session.auth.authenticatedUserId}',
    (message) {
      sendStreamMessage(session, message);
    },
  );
}
```

