TITLE: Creating Custom Health Metric Handler in Dart
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines a custom health metric handler that checks the server health and returns a list of health metrics based on the provided timestamp. It utilizes the Serverpod framework and requires access to the Serverpod instance and the timestamp of the health check.
