TITLE: Generating SQL for One-to-One Relationship in PostgreSQL
DESCRIPTION: Provides the SQL code that Serverpod generates behind the scenes to set up a one-to-one relationship. It includes table creation, unique index, and foreign key constraint definitions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.5.0/06-concepts/06-database/03-relations/01-one-to-one.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

