TITLE: Complex SQL Query for Join Operation
DESCRIPTION: An example of a complex SQL query performing a join operation, used to illustrate changes in query result formatting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-2.4.0/08-upgrading/03-upgrade-to-two.md#2025-04-20_snippet_5

