TITLE: Initializing Session Manager
DESCRIPTION: Setting up the client and session manager for handling authentication state and server communication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/serverpod/serverpod_docs/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-0.9.11/03-concepts/07-authentication.md#2025-04-20_snippet_4

